    "Remove 2x camshaft pulley (2) and (3) from camshaft\n Note position of\nlocating pin on exhaust pulley.\n \n\n\n\n•  \nRemove 2x bolt (1), 2x washer\n \n\n\n\n–\nCounter-hold camshaft at hexagon with open end of spanner\n(4)\n \n\n\n\n\n\n–\nSecond technician required\n \n\n\n\n\n\n–\nDiscard 2x bolt",
